{"tid":1914002,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個女獸醫好似幾大波","createTime":"2020-03-07T08:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T13:39:15.000Z","uid":57308,"like":72,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"76ac7cc9d7fa2e83f61315b71c19499cde220349","tid":1914002,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d1t4v6V.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd1t4v6V.gif&h=f93835db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 係咪光復左香港 五大訴求達到左啦？<br />\n點解仲會俾呢啲垃圾post標題呃到入嚟？<br />\n如果呢個post上唔到熱門 冇哂行動post 我正式宣布呢個運動真係玩完 連登已死<br />\n連我個淺藍老母都問啲暴徒係咪搞完事 外國戰線著哂火咁大粒核彈都冇人理既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6tkOdks.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6tkOdks.png&h=39efadf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔可以當手足係condom？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋揸住佢個春袋 呢粒<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RSHdpsc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSHdpsc.gif&h=f928987b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會令到中共好驚 手足就嚟贏 千祈唔可以中五毛分化撚嘅計 推走熱門行動Post 唔係我哋就嚟輸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4zVeTkE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4zVeTkE.gif&h=f3ccd4c9&s={SIZE}\" /> 五大訴求 缺一不可 煲底見！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EsH9mXW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEsH9mXW.jp